title: Digital LED Number
text: Given a digital LED pattern of a number. You have to find the number and print it. All inputs will be valid as shown.InputInput consists of LED patterns. Each pattern is given in set of fixed number of lines. You have to read input till EOF.OutputPrint the number corresponding to each pattern.ExampleInput:_  _  _  _  _  __| _| _|| ||_||_|_  _||_ |_|  | _|_     _     _||_ |_||_   || |||_|  ||_|  ||_|_  _  _  _     _||_||_||_   ||_||  |  | _|  ||_|Output:232095164610799518
